channel.title: Finally got on Spotify and ITunes!
channel.description:
Hey everyone! Super excited to let you all know that I finally got a track in stores! :indir3ct:
My recent future bass track Stitch got published in stores!!! It would mean the world if you could check it out! Thanks so much :pray:
SoundCloud: https://soundcloud.com/indir3ct/stitch
Spotify: https://exit.sc/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fopen.spotify.com%2Fartist%2F4eAGuZUPSZHBZvDNF1Mu5z
ITunes: https://exit.sc/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fitunes.apple.com%2Fus%2Falbum%2Fstitch%2F1437955306%3Fi%3D1437955309
More tracks will be out soon :wink:
